{"tid":1844540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工要有持久性，香港人我求求你：29號大罷工唔可以淨係一日，要一路罷到真正封關爲止","createTime":"2020-01-26T16:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T01:21:31.000Z","uid":131691,"like":114,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ad3c1143771fd2f7e344e1ab7870ce0538e9e4","tid":1844540,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"一切嘅civil disobedience，個本質就係<strong>政治威脅</strong><br />\n罷工嘅本質，就係<strong>一大班打工仔用自己嘅勞動力生產力去要脅財團/政府</strong><br />\n你一日嘅生產力無咗，就算全港一齊罷，佢都係唔會驚，你嘅要脅亦都無用<br />\n<strong>你幾時聽過一個綁匪會綁架你個仔一日咁大把？過左一日就會自動畀返個仔你？</strong><br />\n<br />\n罷工一定要係一個有持久力嘅要脅<br />\n港共政府嘅無賴程度，我相信大家都已經有目共睹<br />\n所以請做足心理準備，佢會「好打得」咁企硬，同香港人博過<br />\n而香港人，我哋就要作出一個歷史性嘅決定：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分藍黃，爲香港，爲性命，29號大罷工，直至完全封關</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個決定，做咗就冇得反悔，一定要堅持到底<br />\n因爲一縮，港共就會大舉殲滅香港人。"},{"pid":"caa362236e095803e40ef00fa905d532f79d46bd","tid":1844540,"uid":182195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n迫到政府封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8edfb731f683f90ab617ca22b8d625d6108a88","tid":1844540,"uid":258910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34e98ccfe6ea00aeefb35bd4343956f5a55359b8","tid":1844540,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8398076e84d6c406e96e09f7f7d62cbf11d58b","tid":1844540,"uid":65524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d235f19464bd11df809e37563cccf3e366a433","tid":1844540,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"