.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得兩個scenario：<br />\n1. 政府真係跪低，封關，罷工者士氣高漲，我哋就乘勝追擊，升級去五大訴求<br />\n2. 政府唔肯封關，民怨升溫，罷工者「被迫」升級去五大訴求"},{"pid":"a6fcb41c4ab11f223db800626aab0560db25be2d","tid":1844540,"uid":72228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"一定要無了期罷架啦<br />\n因為宜家只差社區爆發<br />\n當社會爆發 大家都係翻唔到工"},{"pid":"08b524cd9dbb6ca7992bc15dfde9b2b96af850da","tid":1844540,"uid":245549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfbd34373e2285231ae2692616059f2b7f107dcc","tid":1844540,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5be74f4986ec4ef023fea7d287a3d3a673a853d0","tid":1844540,"uid":180163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"WITH FIVE DEMANDS"},{"pid":"2bbdc6295f48266755f9f6e7acec9d83e6387029","tid":1844540,"uid":180163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4b537dbb4689e24f1beda1d4d287148e2f8073b","tid":1844540,"uid":180163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"29/1開始一齊罷工"},{"pid":"39f71110fb097cfdfce4297ad48ba68fb259c625","tid":1844540,"uid":298523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"同意，一齊做，推"}]}